The logo needs to be fresh and modern, yet luxurious. Her market demographic is women from 35-60 and we want to use the logo on merchandise. Perhaps update the wave theme and or the signature.
Also, when I had to pick industry, I would have picked yachting or speaking or celebrity. The logo must be clean enough that it can be branded on merchandise.
Also, this logo has to be versatile enough to the transform to Captain Sandy Podcast, Captain Sandy Charities, Captain Sandy Leadership logos … in the future.
Captain Sandy is a super yacht captain and now is going to have a book, speaking engagements on leadership, podcast, merchandise and more. She is on the show Below Deck – Mediterranean and you can look up images of her. Her current logo is an ocean wave in a circle and we want to build off a wave theme.
The logo must convey Captain Sandy is strong, inspiring, a leader, businesswoman, bad-ass, transformative, relevant, passionate, confident, optimistic, dedicated, meaningful change agent,
We will probably want a tag line in the logo – Maybe something like on of those … but I may have to keep thinking or if you have one I am truly interested!
Be the Calm … or Be the Storm
Strong  Transformative  Inspiring
Follow Your True North

title: Design for ice swimming club in Finland
description: We are an ice swimming club based in Espoo, Finland. Enjoying the outdoors, the peace of mind, positive well-being, and sense of achievement that comes from swimming in the hole in the sea ice. Avanto (Finnish=hole in the ice).
other_notes: When you get out of swimming in the hole in the ice, the amazing feelings of wellbeing are really noticeable after you take a few steps on the jetty. We counted 27 planks along when the euphoria kicks in, so we decided to call ourselves Plank 27.
